title: Fractal Analytics IPO: Check GMP, brokerages review, subscription and other details
description: Fractal Analytics' IPO opens today. This is a significant event for India's stock market. It is the first pure-play artificial intelligence company to list. Analysts suggest it is suited for high-risk investors with a long-term view.
